PrecisAmendment to a lease held by ECHO BAY MINES LTD. that adds 0.579 hectares of land to its mining site near Contwoyto Lake in the Northwest Territories which are to be used for the re-alignment of the access road to its road maintenance camp.

precis:
Amendment to a lease held by ECHO BAY MINES LTD. that adds 0.579 hectares
of land to its mining site near Contwoyto Lake in the Northwest Territories
which are to be used for the re-alignment of the access road to its road
maintenance camp.
